<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0006', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:197'>欽定四庫全書　　　　經部四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='197:220'>　周禮復古編　　　　　禮類一<span class='krp-note'>周禮之屬/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='220:226'>　　提要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='226:252'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案周禮復古編一卷宋俞庭椿撰庭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='252:275'>　　　　椿字夀翁臨川人乾通八年進士官古田令</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='275:298'>　　　　是書宋志作三卷今本作一卷標曰陳友仁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='298:321'>　　　　編盖友仁訂正周禮集説而以此書附其後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='321:344'>　　　　也庭椿之説謂五官所屬皆六十不得有羨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='344:370'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0006', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='370:393'>　　　　其羨者皆取以補冬官鑿空臆㫁其謬妄殆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='393:416'>　　　　不足辯又謂天官世婦與春官世婦夏官環</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='416:439'>　　　　人與秋官環人為一官複出當省并之其説</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='439:462'>　　　　似巧而其謬尤甚二世婦與二環人無論職</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='462:485'>　　　　掌各殊即以序官考之天官世婦為王之後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='485:508'>　　　　宫故與九嬪八十一御女皆無官屬至於春</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='508:531'>　　　　官世婦為王之宫官故毎官卿一人下大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='531:554'>　　　　四人中士八人女府二人女史二人奚十六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='554:580'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0006', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='580:603'>　　　　人與天官世婦顯異鄭注以漠之大長秋詹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='603:626'>　　　　事中少府太僕為證其説本確庭椿乃合而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='626:649'>　　　　一之是誤以春官之世婦為婦人也至于司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='649:672'>　　　　馬之環人掌下士六人史二人徒十有二人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='672:695'>　　　　秋官之環人掌中士四人史四人胥四人徒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='695:718'>　　　　四十人若二環人是一官何所屬之中下士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='718:741'>　　　　及史胥徒乃各不同如此耶此好立異説者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='741:764'>　　　　之適以自蔽也然復古之説始于庭椿厥後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='764:790'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0006', 'WYG', '000-2b' );" name="000-2b" class="pb">[000-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='790:813'>　　　　邱葵吴澄皆襲其繆説周禮者遂有冬官不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='813:836'>　　　　亡之一派分門别戸輾轉蔓延其弊至明末</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='836:859'>　　　　而未已故特存其書著竄亂聖經之始為學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='859:881'>　　　　者之炯戒焉乾隆四十六年十月恭校上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='881:913'>　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='913:939'>　　　　　　　　總　校　官　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>　陸　費　墀</span><br/>
</p>
